parameters:
\nc<>What's wrong, Kei-san? You've been on your phone doing
something for a while now.
\nc<>Ah, Candy... I'm doing a little search.

\nc<>I, I mean, I want to know what activities Matsuo-san has
been involved in in the past.

\nc<>Is that about the muscle villain? Leave it alone, meow.
Anyway, a villain's past is never decent, meow.

\nc<>Bad children should be punished, but it's unfortunate that
they can only receive punishment.
\nc<>Thank you, Candy. It's a big difference from some other cat.

\nc<>Well, that's true, but how do you plan to search for it,
meow? The person should already be gone from the studio,
meow.

\nc<>That's right. It's too late to hire a detective and
investigate now. For now, I'm trying to dig as much as I
can...

\nc<>If you connect the traces on the internet, finding the past
activity history is a piece of cake.

\nc<>They're a child who is scared of the future in various ways,
meow...
\nc<>So, is this Matsuo's old channel? Let me see.

\nc<>...Even if it's just flattery, it can't be called a popular
channel, right?

\nc<>I tried my hand at various contents, but none of them stood
out and ended up buried.
\nc<>I'm sorry to say this, but it's a common thing.

\nc<>Ah, but there are still people who leave comments saying
they're waiting!

\nc<>That alone is not enough, meow. If it could be managed with
the support of just one or two fans, I shouldn't have been
so obsessed with the power of villains in the first place,
meow.
\nc<>...No. Sorbet, can you contact that person?
\nc<>It's easy, but... are you really okay?
\nc<>Yeah, I might be able to do this.
\nc<>No, I will definitely make it possible!

\nc<>They keep spouting nothing but logical arguments. I'll
definitely make them take back their words...!
\nc<>I obtained the memory M3: Matsuo's Past.
